if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_productclass')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_productclass
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_productclass */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_productclass (
CID int identity(1,1),
ParentID int null,
Name nvarchar(100) not null,
Icon nvarchar(200) null,
Sort int null,
create_time datetime not null default getdate(),
create_user_id bigint not null,
edit_time datetime not null default getdate(),
edit_user_id bigint not null,
del_flag bit not null default 1,
del_time datetime null,
del_user_id bigint null,
remark nvarchar(255) null,
constraint PK_BASE_PRODUCTCLASS primary key (CID)
)
go
